### 2. COMPONENTES CON BEM + @APPLY

```css
/* Componente encapsulado */
.card-tier {
  @apply bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm transition-all;
  transition: var(--transition-smooth);
}

.card-tier__title {
  @apply text-2xl font-bold mb-4;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
}

.card-tier__button {
  @apply px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-center inline-block;
  background-color: var(--color-accent);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

/* Modificador destacado */
.card-tier--featured {
  @apply ring-2 ring-offset-2;
}
```

